                <div style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:#333333; margin:0; padding:0 0 15px 0; line-height:20px;">If you use a direct URL to link to either program, this will not change. When the switch is made, we will send an email confirming all the details.</div>
                
